  "texts": [
    "(1) The ProAcT propose to model the relations between two consecutive training episodes by introducing cross-task prototypes.",
    "Essentially, during training process, ProAcT utilize K*2 and Q*2 instances to construct prototypes in the N-Way-K-shot setting.",
    "In addition, the ProAcT formulates FSED into a event classification task, the labels of the query set were exposed to construct the prototypes in training process comparing with event detection.",
    "Therefore, we have reimplemented it as event detection task.",
    "(2) HCL-TAT proposed a hybrid contrastive learning method to generate more discriminative representations for both the support and query sets."
  ],
